C: TIMSORT
T: MAIN
M: TIMSORT ARRAY, MINSIZE
S: MAIN,#A,MAIN

C: MERGESORT
M: MERGESORT ARRAY, MINSIZE
S: $A,#L,MERGESORT

C: INSERTIONSORT
M: INSERTIONSORT ARRAY
S: $A,#S,INSERTIONSORT

C: MERGE
M: MERGE LEFT, RIGHT
S: $L,$R,#M,MERGE

T: INPUT
R: ARRAY = [5, 2, 8, 1, 9, 3]
R: MINSIZE = 32

T: PROCESS
R: RESULT = TIMSORT(ARRAY, MINSIZE)

T: OUTPUT
R: PRINT RESULT
